-1 GATE~
/---------------------------------------------------------------------\
|       GATE                                                          |
\---------------------------------------------------------------------/

The Gate spell is a magic born of the void, allowing the caster to
literally tear a hole in the fabric of the material plane, stepping
directly through to the void. From the void, with focus born of
magical concentration, the caster is able to step out of the void,
through a doorway to elsewhere in the material plane. The spell
requires a target to focus the path through the void. No immortal
can be used, and a fellow adventurer that is protected by the gods
would be immune if they wished it. The victim has a chance to avoid
being used as an endpoint, and many places cannot be gated to at all.
Lastly, the trip is not without price, and the trip through the void
can injure the caster.

~

